47:44.781 --> 47:49.828
I don't want you to feel
like you have no one to talk to.

47:50.036 --> 47:54.583
Your parents, or girl problems ...

47:54.750 --> 48:02.549
Here's my home phone.
Anything at all, you call me.

48:03.133 --> 48:07.929
Call me. Deal?

48:08.138 --> 48:12.184
I'm telling you, if you
get past this little hurdle, -

48:12.350 --> 48:16.938
