- You've got some balls!

48:58.355 --> 49:03.819
- You played it beautifully.
- I could've busted you right there.

49:03.985 --> 49:09.449
Yes, you could have, but did not.
Why was that?

49:11.827 --> 49:16.373
Your Edward French
won't give you any more trouble.

49:16.540 --> 49:21.586
