do something that can't be done.

49:25.715 --> 49:31.680
It can and it will. You simply
have to work. No more stories.

49:31.888 --> 49:35.559
- Stop screwing around.
- I don't take orders from you.

49:35.726 --> 49:40.689
- You do now.
- I can just pick up the phone.

49:40.856 --> 49:43.900
